Megatron realised what was happening, and in a split second, his eyes
roared to life, shinning brightly. He clutched the ground, the quickly
rolloed out of the blade's line of fire, firring in the general
direction of Unitron, at his legs, hoping to go under Firestrike. If
only Firestrike knew what was happening. Oh well, he could be repaired,
and his protective form for my life is almost touching.
